    {
      "id": "PopularPost8142",
      "post_content": "I actually used to love this card...if anything I liked it for its flavor text. Most players, myself included, would rather pay the extra mana for a [Prodigal Pyromancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Pyromancer). But the fact it comes out on turn 2 means it can deal with your opponent's weenies they dropped turn 1 much faster, which ultimately means less damage to you. This card is really good with effects that trigger when you hit a player, as they can trigger twice per turn if you use it with this guy (since he hits you for damage, not loss of life).",
      "posted_by": "kitsunewarlock",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost8142\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I actually used to love this card...if anything I liked it for its flavor text.  Most players, myself included, would rather pay the extra mana for a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Prodigal Pyromancer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prodigal Pyromancer\">Prodigal Pyromancer</a>.  But the fact it comes out on turn 2 means it can deal with your opponent's weenies they dropped turn 1 much faster, which ultimately means less damage to you.  This card is really good with effects that trigger when you hit a player, as they can trigger twice per turn if you use it with this guy (since he hits you for damage, not loss of life).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '8142'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy486\">kitsunewarlock</span>\r\n                                (6/2/2009 3:18:57 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater